    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver despite showing its age. The engine and transmission are functional, though the car has high mileage and would benefit from a tune-up and some suspension work to restore its original ride quality. The body has several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear fender, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and carpet. It is a solid choice for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a few cosmetic and mechanical imperfections.",
