    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine is strong and responsive, and the transmission shifts smoothly, ensuring a dependable driving experience. While there may be some minor signs of normal wear and tear consistent with its age, the interior is clean and the exterior retains a solid appearance. It is a reliable choice for anyone seeking a quality used car that is ready for the road.",
