    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is looking for a dedicated new owner to give it the TLC it needs. While it's currently in poor condition and requires significant mechanical and cosmetic work, it represents a fantastic opportunity to own a car at a budget-friendly price. If you're looking for a rewarding restoration project, this is the perfect canvas for you!",
